				<p><p>Based on Ian C.'s response:</p>

<p>Would it be possible to rename <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/photos" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;photos&#39;" rel="tag">photos</a> to <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/photography" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;photography&#39;" rel="tag">photography</a> and then create a new <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/photos" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;photos&#39;" rel="tag">photos</a> tag that was a synonym to <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/photos.app" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;photos.app&#39;" rel="tag">photos.app</a>? That would:</p>

